different things.

57
00:05:30,622 --> 00:05:32,082
While we’re on the subject,

58
00:05:32,165 --> 00:05:33,955
where’s Miina staying?

59
00:05:34,042 --> 00:05:36,172
‐ She’s staying with
one of her classmates.

60
00:05:36,294 --> 00:05:38,464
Her name is Haruko Shido.

61
00:05:38,547 --> 00:05:39,757
‐ Haruko?

62
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:43,180
‐ Yeah, she’s just a
girl who’s in her class.

