83
00:06:34,728 --> 00:06:36,978
It just feels like it, you know.

84
00:06:37,063 --> 00:06:39,323
It just feels like it.

85
00:06:39,399 --> 00:06:41,109
‐ Haruko, do you
think that maybe

86
00:06:41,234 --> 00:06:42,744
